name: 2010-noaa-ortho-rectified-mosaic-from-color-aerial-imagery-of-beaumont-orange-port-authur
notes: This data set contains ortho-rectified mosaic tiles, created as a product from the NOAA Integrated Ocean and Coastal Mapping (IOCM) initiative of BEAUMONT, ORANGE, PORT AUTHUR. The source imagery was acquired on March 12, 2010 and March 13, 2010. The true color images were acquired with an Applanix Digital Sensor System (DSS). The original images were acquired at a higher resolution than the final ortho-rectified mosaic.
